  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.9">
<l>ūṭēṟu kañcaṉoṭu mallum villu moṇkariyu muruḷcakaṭu muṭaiyac ceṟṟa</l>
<l>nīṭēṟu peruvalittō ḷuṭaiya veṉṟi nilavupukaḻ nēmiyaṅkai neṭiyōṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>cēṭēṟu poḻiltaḻuvu meḻilkoḷ vītit tiruviḻavil maṇiyaṇinta tiṇṇai tōṟum</l>
<l>āṭēṟu malarkkuḻalār payiluñ celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The tall one with very long, large, strong arms, in whose fine hand</l>
<l rend="indent">is the renowned discus whose victories shine,</l>
<l>Who raged at extremely resentful Kaṁsa, the wrestlers, the bow,</l>
<l rend="indent">the dazzling elephant, and the rolling cart so that they [all] were ruined,</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where dwell girls with curls where flowers sway madly,</l>
<l>In every verandah decorated with jewels at sacred festivals in colorful streets</l>
<l rend="indent">embraced by beautiful groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
